Onboarding.WhatIsOONIProbe.Title: Ni nini OONI Probe?
Onboarding.WhatIsOONIProbe.Paragraph:
Programu yako ya kupima udhibiti wa mtandao.

Je! Tovuti na programu za media ya kijamii zimezuiwa? Je! Muunganisho wako wa mtandao uko polepole sana?

Endesha uchunguzi wa OONI kujua!
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Title: Tunaelekea!
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.1: Takwimu za OONI zimechapishwa wazi na zitajumuisha habari ya mtandao wako.
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.2: Mtu yeyote anayefuatilia shughuli zako za mtandao(kwa mfano serikali au ISP)ataona kwamba unatumia OONI Probe
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.3: Unaweza kujaribu tovuti zilizopigwa marufuku (lakini unaweza kuchagua tovuti gani za kujaribu).
Onboarding.PopQuiz.Title: Jaribio la Pop
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Title: Swali 1/2
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Question: Ikiwa mtu anafuatilia shughuli zangu za mtandao, ataona kuwa ninaendesha OONI Probe.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Wrong.Title: Onyo
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Wrong.Paragraph: Probe ya OONI sio zana ya faragha. Mtu yeyote anayefuatilia shughuli zako za mtandao ataona ni programu ipi unayoendesha.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Title: Swali 2/2
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Question: Kila wakati ninapoendesha OONI Probe, data ya mtandao ninayokusanya itachapishwa kiatomati.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Wrong.Title: Onyo
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Wrong.Paragraph: Ili kuongeza uwazi wa udhibiti wa mtandao, data ya mtandao ya watumiaji wote wa OONI Probe inachapishwa kiatomati (isipokuwa wata chagua katika mipangilio).
Onboarding.AutomatedTesting.Title: Upimaji wa kiotomatiki
Onboarding.AutomatedTesting.Paragraph:
To measure internet censorship every day, please enable automated testing so that OONI Probe can run tests periodically.

Don't worry, we'll be mindful of battery usage. 

You can disable automated testing from the settings at any time.
Onboarding.Crash.Title: Taarifa ya Ajali
Onboarding.Crash.Paragraph:
Ili kuboresha OONI Probe tungependa kukusanya ripoti zisizojulikana za ajali wakati programu haifanyi kazi vizuri.

Je! Ungependa kuchagua kutuma ripoti za ajali kwa timu ya maendeleo ya OONI?
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Title: Mipangilio chaguomsingi
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Bullet.1: Nambari ya nchi (k.m. IT ya Italia
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Bullet.2: Maelezo ya mtandao (pamoja na Nambari ya Mfumo wa Uhuru)
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Paragraph:
Tunafanya bidii yetu kutochapisha anwani yako ya IP au habari nyingine yoyote inayoweza kujitambulisha kibinafsi.

Jifunze zaidi kupitia [Sera ya Takwimu ya OONI] (https://ooni.org/about/data-policy/).
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Paragraph.1: Kwa kugonga "Sawa", utashiriki ripoti za ajali ili kutusaidia kuboresha Probe ya OONI.

Dashboard.Card.Subtitle: Gonga kadi kwa zaidi
Dashboard.Websites.Overview.Paragraph:
Angalia kama tovuti zimezuiwa kwa kutumia [Mtihani wa Kuunganishwa Wavuti](https://ooni.org/nettest/web-kuunganishwa/).

Kila wakati unapogusa Run, unajaribu tovuti tofauti kutoka kwa Maabara ya Citizen [ya kimataifa](orodha https://github.com/citizenlab/test / blob / bwana / orodha / kimataifa.csv) na [nchi maalum](orodha https://github.com/citizenlab/test/mti / bwana / orodha) orodha ya mtihani.

Ili kujaribu tovuti za chaguo lako, gusa kitufe cha Chagua tovuti au chagua makundi ya tovuti kupitia mipangilio ya kadi hii. 

Mtihani huu unapima ikiwa tovuti zimefungwa kwa njia ya DNS kutatiza, TCP / IP kuzuia au kwa mhimili wa HTTP wazi.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) na [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).

.
Dashboard.Websites.Overview.Paragraph.De:
Angalia ikiwa tovuti zimezuiwa kutumia OONI's [Mtihani wa Muunganisho wa Wavuti] (https://ooni.org/nettest/web-connectivity/).

Utajaribu tovuti zilizojumuishwa katika Maabara ya Citizen [ya kimataifa] (https://github.com/citizenlab/test-lists/blob/master/lists/global.csv) na [maalum kwa nchi] (https: // github .com / Citizlab / orodha za mtihani / mti / bwana / orodha) orodha za majaribio.

Jaribio hili linapima ikiwa tovuti zimezuiwa kwa njia ya kukwamisha DNS, kuzuia TCP / IP au kwa wakala wa uwazi wa HTTP.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.Performance.Card.Description: Jaribu kasi ya mtandao wako na utendaji
Dashboard.Performance.Overview.Paragraph:
Pima kasi na utendaji wa mtandao wako kwa kutumia jaribio la [NDT] (https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/).

Pima utiririshaji wa video ukitumia jaribio la [DASH] (https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/).

Vipimo hivi hutumia data kulingana na kasi ya mtandao wako.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/).

Kanusho: Majaribio haya yanategemea seva za mtu mwingine. Kwa hivyo hatuwezi kuhakikisha kuwa anwani yako ya IP haitakusanywa.

Kwa kufanya majaribio kwenye kadi hii, uta:

- Pima kasi na utendaji wa mtandao wako ([NDT] (https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/) mtihani)
- Pima utiririshaji wa video ([DASH] (https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/) mtihani)
- Angalia uwepo wa [teknolojia za kati] -request-line /) na [Udhibiti wa Shamba la kichwa cha HTTP] (https://ooni.org/nettest/http-header-field-manipulation/) vipimo)

Vipimo hivi hutumia data kulingana na kasi ya mtandao wako.

Matokeo yako ya mtihani yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/).

** Kanusho: ** Jaribio la [NDT] (https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/) na [DASH] (https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/) hufanywa dhidi ya seva za mtu wa tatu iliyotolewa na [Maabara ya Upimaji (M-Lab)] (https://www.measurementlab.net/). Ikiwa utafanya majaribio haya, M-Lab itakusanya na kuchapisha anwani yako ya IP (kwa sababu za utafiti), bila kujali mipangilio yako ya OONI Probe. Pata maelezo zaidi kuhusu utawala wa data wa M-Lab kupitia [taarifa ya faragha] (https://www.measurementlab.net/privacy/).
Dashboard.Middleboxes.Card.Description: Gundua visanduku vya kati kwenye mtandao wako
Dashboard.Middleboxes.Overview.Paragraph:
Watoa Huduma za Mtandao mara nyingi hutumia vifaa vya mtandao (visanduku vya kati) kwa madhumuni anuwai ya mitandao (kama kuhifadhi akiba). Wakati mwingine sanduku hizi za kati hutumiwa kutekeleza udhibiti wa mtandao na / au ufuatiliaji.

Pata visanduku vya kati katika mtandao wako ukitumia OONI ya [Mstari wa Ombi batili wa HTTP] (https://ooni.org/nettest/http-invalid-request-line/) na [Udhibiti wa Shamba la Kichwa cha HTTP] (https://ooni.org/nettest / http-kichwa-shamba-kudanganywa /) vipimo.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/)
Dashboard.InstantMessaging.Card.Descript: Jaribu uzuiaji wa programu za ujumbe wa papo hapo
Dashboard.InstantMessaging.Overview.Para:
Angalia ikiwa [WhatsApp] (https://ooni.org/nettest/whatsapp/), [Facebook Messenger] (https://ooni.org/nettest/facebook-messenger/), [Telegram] (https: // ooni .org / nettest / telegram /), na [Signal] (https://ooni.org/nettest/signal) zimezuiwa.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.Circumvention.Card.Description: Jaribu kuzuia vifaa vya kuzuia uzuiaji
Dashboard.Circumvention.Overview.Paragra:
Angalia ikiwa [Psiphon] (https://ooni.org/nettest/psiphon/), [Tor] (https://ooni.org/nettest/tor/) au [RiseupVPN] (https://ooni.org/ nettest / riseupvpn /) zimezuiwa.

Matokeo yako yatachapishwa kwenye [OONI Explorer] (https://explorer.ooni.org/) na [OONI API] (https://api.ooni.io/).

Settings.About.Label: Kuhusu OONI
Settings.About.Content.Paragraph:
Uchunguzi wa Wazi wa Uingiliano wa Mtandao (OONI) ni mradi wa programu ya bure chini ya Mradi wa Tor ambao unakusudia kuongeza uwazi wa udhibiti wa mtandao kote ulimwenguni.

Tangu 2012, jamii ya kimataifa ya OONI imekuwa ikipima mitandao katika nchi zaidi ya 200. Baadhi ya vipimo hivi hutumika kama ushahidi wa udhibiti wa mtandao.

Settings.AutomatedTesting.RunAutomatical:
By enabling automatic testing, OONI Probe tests will run automatically multiple times per day. Your test results will automatically get published on OONI Explorer: https://explorer.ooni.org/ 

Important: If you have a VPN enabled, OONI Probe will not run tests automatically. Please turn off your VPN for automated OONI Probe testing. Learn more: https://ooni.org/support/faq/#can-i-run-ooni-probe-over-a-vpn
